If you actually want to render the HTML *as* HTML inside the document, then using `innerHTML` is acceptable for this task - assuming you fully-trust the source of the AJAX response not to return malicious HTML that might contain scripts (and regardless, [you should set a `Content-Security-Policy` on your document so browsers won&#39;t execute any added scripts anyway][1]):

